<datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="545">
<subfield code="a">
Margarita Mazo is a professor emerita at the Ohio State University, where she founded a program in Cognitive Ethnomusicology. She holds a PhD from the Leningrad (St. Petersburg) Conservatory where her research focused on Russian music. She has held teaching positions at the Leningrad (St. Petersburg) Conservatory, the New England Conservatory of Music, and Harvard University.
</subfield>
</datafield>
